"11": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "11",
&"next_id": "12",
&"text": "Hello??",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"12": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "12",
&"next_id": "13",
&"text": "Sorry! I'm back 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"13": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "13",
&"next_id": "14",
&"text": "What was that about?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"14": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "14",
&"next_id": "15",
&"text": "Nothing nothing! He just wanted to show me something ☺️",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"15": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "15",
&"next_id": "16",
&"text": "Please don't say anything that might embarass me or lead him on 🙄",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"16": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "16",
&"next_id": "17",
&"text": "I don't want to deal with any of that, I'm no good at it",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"17": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "17",
&"next_id": "18",
&"text": "Oh don't worry, he didn't mention you at all actually",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"18": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "18",
&"next_id": "19",
&"text": "Huh? Really? Then why? 🤔",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"19": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "19",
&"next_id": "20",
&"text": "I guess that's a relief",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"2": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "2",
&"next_id": "3",
&"text": "You're doing it again 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"20": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "20",
&"next_id": "21",
&"text": "Of course! There really is nothing to worry about baby 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"21": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "21",
&"next_id": "22",
&"text": "He won't be commenting or asking you out anymore",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"22": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "22",
&"next_id": "23",
&"text": "Anyway, forget about that",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"23": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "23",
&"next_id": "24",
&"text": "Okie dokes, if you say so",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"24": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "24",
&"next_id": "25",
&"text": "What are you doing right now anyway?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"25": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "25",
&"next_id": "26",
&"text": "Just having dinner sweetie",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"26": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "26",
&"next_id": "27",
&"text": "img: mom/4",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"27": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "27",
&"next_id": "28",
&"text": "Your face is red mom, do you have a fever or something?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"28": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "28",
&"next_id": "29",
&"text": "Oh is it?? Don't mind that honey",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"29": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "29",
&"next_id": "30",
&"text": "How was your date today? Tell me everything!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"3": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "3",
&"next_id": "4",
&"text": "Doing what honey? 😊",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"30": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "30",
&"next_id": "31",
&"text": "It was so good 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"31": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "31",
&"next_id": "32",
&"text": "We went to the park and just spent the whole day together",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"32": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "32",
&"next_id": "33",
&"text": "It was perfect weather too",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"33": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "33",
&"next_id": "34",
&"text": "That sounds wonderful honey",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"34": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "34",
&"next_id": "35",
&"text": "Uhm.. can I ask you something? 🙃",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"35": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "35",
&"next_id": "36",
&"text": "Of course! You can ask me anything",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"36": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "36",
&"next_id": "37",
&"text": "OMG YES",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"37": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "37",
&"next_id": "38",
&"text": "Did you kiss him? Your first boyfriend?? 😶",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"38": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "38",
&"next_id": "39",
&"text": "Of course I did silly",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"39": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "39",
&"next_id": "40",
&"text": "What was it like?? 🥺",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"4": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "4",
&"next_id": "5",
&"text": "Commenting on my posts!! You said you wouldn't!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"40": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "40",
&"next_id": "41",
&"text": "It was really soft",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"41": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "41",
&"next_id": "42",
&"text": "Like the gentlest thing in the world",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"42": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "42",
&"next_id": "43",
&"text": "Really? 🥹",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"43": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "43",
&"next_id": "44",
&"text": "Mhmm? Did you never kiss your boyfriend? I thought you would have by now? 😄",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"44": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "44",
&"next_id": "45",
&"text": "👉👈 I dunno, just never thought of it",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"45": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "45",
&"next_id": "46",
&"text": "But I want to! I just don't know how... or where? Or if I'm ready yet",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"46": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "46",
&"next_id": "47",
&"text": "Where did you do it mom? 😳",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"47": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "47",
&"next_id": "48",
&"text": "I think I have a picture on my phone",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"48": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "48",
&"next_id": "49",
&"text": "img: mom/5",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"49": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "49",
&"next_id": "50",
&"text": "Omg this is adorable",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"5": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "5",
&"next_id": "6",
&"text": "And you're talking to that guy AGAIN",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"50": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "50",
&"next_id": "51",
&"text": "Mhmm! We actually went to the beach and watched the sunset",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"51": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "51",
&"next_id": "52",
&"text": "I thought my heart was going to explode but he was even more nervous than I was ☺️",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"52": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "52",
&"next_id": "53",
&"text": "I didn't know what to do so I just closed my eyes and made it easy for him haha",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"53": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "53",
&"next_id": "54",
&"text": "That's so cute I'm gonna cry 😭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"54": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "54",
&"next_id": "55",
&"text": "It was! His hands were super shaky and sweaty 😆",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"55": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "55",
&"next_id": "56",
&"text": "I wish he'd been a little more assertive but every boy is different 😊",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"56": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "56",
&"next_id": "57",
&"text": "What do you mean?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"57": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "57",
&"next_id": "58",
&"text": "I think the kisses I really best remember are more feisty 😆 I love when a guy needs to kiss me so he comes and takes it hehe 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"58": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "58",
&"next_id": "59",
&"text": "But I didn't mind",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"59": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "59",
&"next_id": "60",
&"text": "I don't think I could ever do that 🙈",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"6": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "6",
&"next_id": "7",
&"text": "Oh! I'm sorry sweetheart",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"60": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "60",
&"next_id": "61",
&"text": "There's no rush though honey",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"61": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "61",
&"next_id": "62",
&"text": "You will when you're ready honey 😘 You're momma's girl 💪",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"62": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "62",
&"next_id": "63",
&"text": "But I'm kind of curious mom",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"63": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "63",
&"next_id": "64",
&"text": "You said dad came after your first boyfriend 🤔",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"64": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "64",
&"next_id": "65",
&"text": "What happened to the first guy and how did you meet dad?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"65": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "65",
&"next_id": "66",
&"text": "Well... ☺️",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"66": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "66",
&"next_id": "67",
&"text": "Your dad was another student at our college",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"67": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "67",
&"next_id": "68",
&"text": "I hadn't met him but I heard of him because he would always pop up in the college news letter as part of the wrestling team",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"68": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "68",
&"next_id": "69",
&"text": "He was quite popular you know",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"69": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "69",
&"next_id": "70",
&"text": "Really?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"7": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "7",
&"next_id": "8",
&"text": "I was being polite and he messaged me directly to apologize!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"70": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "70",
&"next_id": "71",
&"text": "I remember something like that when I was little",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"71": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "71",
&"next_id": "72",
&"text": "Mhmm! He used to do personal training before we got the divorce",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"72": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "72",
&"next_id": "73",
&"text": "So you were still with your boyfriend when you met dad, right? 🤔",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"73": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "73",
&"next_id": "74",
&"text": "I was",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"74": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "74",
&"next_id": "75",
&"text": "Did they know each other?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"75": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "75",
&"next_id": "76",
&"text": "They did.. 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"76": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "76",
&"next_id": "77",
&"text": "They weren't exactly friends though",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"77": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "77",
&"next_id": "78",
&"text": "What do you mean?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"78": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "78",
&"next_id": "79",
&"text": "They just didn't like each other much",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"79": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "79",
&"next_id": "80",
&"text": "And I loved my boyfriend, I really did",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"8": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "8",
&"next_id": "9",
&"text": "He direct messaged you??",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"80": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "80",
&"next_id": "81",
&"text": "So I'd get really annoyed with your dad about how he treated my boyfriend at the time",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"81": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "81",
&"next_id": "82",
&"text": "Your dad would make fun of him and push him around sometimes",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"82": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "82",
&"next_id": "83",
&"text": "Dad was always a meanie huh 😒",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"83": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "83",
&"next_id": "84",
&"text": "He was 🙄 I had to step in and tell him to go away",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"84": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "84",
&"next_id": "85",
&"text": "I could kind of imagine that 😆",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"85": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "85",
&"next_id": "86",
&"text": "You're scary when you're mad 😨",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"86": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "86",
&"next_id": "87",
&"text": "Seriously 😤",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"87": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "87",
&"next_id": "88",
&"text": "img: mom/6",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"88": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "88",
&"next_id": "89",
&"text": "I'd give him this look and he would back right off cause nobody messes with your mom 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"89": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "89",
&"next_id": "90",
&"text": "Omg 😂",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"9": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "9",
&"next_id": "10",
&"text": "Hold on one second honey",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"90": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "90",
&"next_id": "91",
&"text": "My angry face looks cute and not serious at all 🙄🥹 I'm so jealous",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"91": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "91",
&"next_id": "92",
&"text": "I hope you never have to use that face hehe 🩷",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"92": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "92",
&"next_id": "93",
&"text": "Well I just finished up and have to do a grocery run alright baby?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"93": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "93",
&"next_id": "94",
&"text": "Awwh, I have so many questions still 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"94": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "94",
&"next_id": "95",
&"text": "I know! I wish I could answer them all in one go but your mom's a busy lady!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"95": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "95",
&"next_id": "96",
&"text": "And you better be studying too! 😠",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"96": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "96",
&"next_id": "97",
&"text": "Eep, that face!!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"97": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "97",
&"next_id": "98",
&"text": "And make sure you take breaks and have lots of fun okay? 😚😚",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"98": {
&"character": "Mom",
&"id": "98",
&"next_id": "99",
&"text": "College only happens once you know! 🤭",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"99": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "99",
&"next_id": "100",
&"text": "I'll try mom, thanks",
&"type": "dialogue"
}
}
raw_text = "~ start
PlayerM: Mom
PlayerM: You're doing it again 😭
Mom: Doing what honey? 😊
PlayerM: Commenting on my posts!! You said you wouldn't!
PlayerM: And you're talking to that guy AGAIN
Mom: Oh! I'm sorry sweetheart
Mom: I was being polite and he messaged me directly to apologize!
PlayerM: He direct messaged you??
Mom: Hold on one second honey
PlayerM: Mom??
PlayerM: Hello??
Mom: Sorry! I'm back 😅
PlayerM: What was that about?
Mom: Nothing nothing! He just wanted to show me something ☺️
PlayerM: Please don't say anything that might embarass me or lead him on 🙄
PlayerM: I don't want to deal with any of that, I'm no good at it
Mom: Oh don't worry, he didn't mention you at all actually
PlayerM: Huh? Really? Then why? 🤔
PlayerM: I guess that's a relief
Mom: Of course! There really is nothing to worry about baby 🥰 
Mom: He won't be commenting or asking you out anymore
Mom: Anyway, forget about that
PlayerM: Okie dokes, if you say so
PlayerM: What are you doing right now anyway?
Mom: Just having dinner sweetie
Mom: img: mom/4
PlayerM: Your face is red mom, do you have a fever or something?
Mom: Oh is it?? Don't mind that honey
Mom: How was your date today? Tell me everything!
PlayerM: It was so good 🥰
PlayerM: We went to the park and just spent the whole day together
PlayerM: It was perfect weather too
Mom: That sounds wonderful honey
PlayerM: Uhm.. can I ask you something? 🙃
Mom: Of course! You can ask me anything
PlayerM: OMG YES
PlayerM: Did you kiss him? Your first boyfriend?? 😶
Mom: Of course I did silly
PlayerM: What was it like?? 🥺
Mom: It was really soft
Mom: Like the gentlest thing in the world
PlayerM: Really? 🥹
Mom: Mhmm? Did you never kiss your boyfriend? I thought you would have by now? 😄
PlayerM: 👉👈 I dunno, just never thought of it
PlayerM: But I want to! I just don't know how... or where? Or if I'm ready yet
PlayerM: Where did you do it mom? 😳
Mom: I think I have a picture on my phone
Mom: img: mom/5
PlayerM: Omg this is adorable
Mom: Mhmm! We actually went to the beach and watched the sunset
Mom: I thought my heart was going to explode but he was even more nervous than I was ☺️
Mom: I didn't know what to do so I just closed my eyes and made it easy for him haha
PlayerM: That's so cute I'm gonna cry 😭
Mom: It was! His hands were super shaky and sweaty 😆
Mom: I wish he'd been a little more assertive but every boy is different 😊
PlayerM: What do you mean?
Mom: I think the kisses I really best remember are more feisty 😆 I love when a guy needs to kiss me so he comes and takes it hehe 🤭
Mom: But I didn't mind
PlayerM: I don't think I could ever do that 🙈
Mom: There's no rush though honey
Mom: You will when you're ready honey 😘 You're momma's girl 💪
PlayerM: But I'm kind of curious mom
PlayerM: You said dad came after your first boyfriend 🤔
PlayerM: What happened to the first guy and how did you meet dad?
